snippet.title: IFSCL - 10-11th Anniversary Trailer | Code Lyoko Game
snippet.description:
PLAY THE GAME : http://bit.ly/websiteIFSCL
A short video teaser of the epic video planned for Early 2021 for my 10+ years code lyoko fangame: the IFSCL. (Anniversary is originally on April 13th 2010)
Changelog: http://bit.ly/changelogIFSCL 
FR/EN Discord : http://bit.ly/discordIFSCL | 
Facebook: http://bit.ly/facebookIFSCL

Original music recording and sounds editing by Cinemorphique for IFSCL.
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCTSdzEE91XoVpnml-VP-1Ug
Based of incidental music of No Ordinary Family, by Blake Nelly.

#trailer  #ifscl  #codelyoko  #fangame
